<br>
fast forward to Planes of Power era.<br>
anyone with a gate spell can now port to nearly any destination achievable by wizards, or close. most of the other areas are often infrequent to visit, ie loy and hateplane. thus anyone with a locket of escape, binden concerettia, and gate potion can have a pocket wizard for travel at 95% of what our ports do.<br>
<br>
